Harrell of the 40th and others
A RESOLUTION
1 Commending and congratulating Mother Willie Bell Beatles; and for other purposes.
2 WHEREAS, Mother Willie Bell Beatles was born on March 14, 1928, in Fayette County,
3 Georgia, and this year she enjoys the rare distinction of celebrating her 97th birthday; and
4 WHEREAS, the devotion, patience, and understanding she has demonstrated have provided
5 the foundation of success from which her family members have developed and flourished,
6 as evidenced by her 10 wonderful children, 20 outstanding grandchildren, 26 exceptional
7 great-grandchildren, and seven magnificent great-great-grandchildren; and
8 WHEREAS, she has lived in the Thomasville community for 68 years and has worshiped at
9 First Mount Selah Baptist Church for 71 years, where she serves faithfully on the Mother's
10 Board, advises fellow members, and remains active in every aspect of church life; and
11 WHEREAS, this distinguished gentlewoman has given inspiration to many through her high
12 ideals, morals, and deep concern for her fellow citizens; and
